name: Fin
description: Edition of 15/15. From my series "Running from Something, Looking for Something", I wanted to explore the effects of being isolated from technology, throwing myself into a world of ethereal landscapes devoid of any intentions. Shot in Iceland, 2017 with a Leica M2 / Kodak Tri-X. (https://jonathanliu.net/running/) (1885 x 1885)
